HIP has been successfully treating mould across the West GTA and consulting on projects across North America since 2007.  
 
Our patent-pending treat-in-place mould eradication process is the only of its kind:
 
It is safe and environmentally-friendly.  
 
It can be performed any time of year.
 
It is done with minimum impact to the building structure and its people and critters.
 
We operate free of any identifiers -- no nosy neighbours knowing what work you are having done!
